Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_sata_lane::_tx_preemph#

SATA TX preemphasis at Gen 1, 2 and 3 speeds. The values of the CSR fields in these registers do not change during chip warm or soft resets. * PREEMPH(0) is for Gen1. * PREEMPH(1) is for Gen2. * PREEMPH(2) is for Gen3.
